  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_095_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これが魔科学兵器の力なんだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So this is the power of Magitech weapons...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41428</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_095_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>多くの人の命を奪って、さらに星のマナも
食らいつくす、それが魔科学兵器、か……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A weapon capable of not only slaughtering countless people but also destroying the entire planet by Mana exhaustion...that's what a Magitech weapon is.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41504</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_095_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>禁止して正解だったよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Good thing it's forbidden for use!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41592</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_095_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、これも失敗があっての答え……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yet... to fire it is a mistake in and out of itself...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_095_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>たくさんの人が犠牲になってから
ダメだったって気付く……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's impossible to be ignorant the thousands, let alone millions, of possible victims...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_095_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>人はそうして過ちを過ちとして
認めるんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Humans are capable of ignoring its mistakes and believing this time it'll be fine.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41928</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_095_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そのためにこの世界の歴史も一度、
変えられなければならなかった、&lt;Cless&gt;たちの手で</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That fallacy leads to history repeating itself time and time again, refusing to learn...As &lt;Cless&gt; and the others know...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
